### Description

https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/issues/14777 is said to have been fixed by https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/pull/14951. Unfortunately I am having the same problem as #14777.

If I use ng serve -c es5 the app displays as expected in IE 11 However, I am unable to get the app to run in IE 11 under IIS.


**References:**
[https://stackoverflow.com/questions/56379067/how-do-i-support-internet-explorer-in-an-angular-8-application](url)
[https://social.msdn.microsoft.com/Forums/en-US/42683470-1d97-4fc1-8248-7cd030bf84e8/how-to-let-angular-8-app-work-in-internet-explorer-11?forum=iewebdevelopment](url)

